OL,3,CPolice investigating after shot fired
OL,4,Cat home in Ballynahinch
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a shot
OL,7,Fwas fired at a property in Co Down.
OL,9,FThe PSNI said they received a report
OL,10,Fafter 11.30pm on Friday that a shot
OL,11,Fhad been fired at the rear door of a
OL,12,Fresidential property in the vicinity
OL,13,Fof Isle of Shinney Walk in
OL,14,FBallynahinch.
OL,16,FPolice said when they attended the
OL,17,Fscene they saw what appeared to be
OL,18,Fshotgun pellet holes in the door and
OL,19,Fsmashed glass.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
