OL,3,CPolice investigating after shot fired
OL,4,Cat home in Ballynahinch
OL,6,FPolice are appealing to anyone who was
OL,7,Fin the area at the time, who may have
OL,8,Fseen the incident happen or who may
OL,9,Fhave information to assist with the
OL,10,Finvestigation, to get in touch on 101
OL,11,Fquoting reference 1720 of March 13.
